#: ../../preinstall.rst:150
msgid ""
"**NVIDIA:** 3D acceleration on NVIDIA is provided by native FreeBSD drivers."
" If an NVIDIA video card is detected, an :guilabel:`nVidia settings` icon "
"will be added to :guilabel:`Browse Applications` for managing NVIDIA "
"settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../preinstall.rst:164
msgid ""
"**Optimus:** At this time there is no switching support between the two "
"graphics adapters provided by Optimus. Optimus implementations vary, so "
"|trueos| may or may not be able to successfully load a graphics driver on "
"hardware. If a blank screen shows after installation, check the BIOS to see "
"if it has an option to disable one of the graphics adapters or to set "
"\"discrete\" mode. If the BIOS does not provide a discrete mode, |trueos| "
"will default to the 3D Intel driver and disable NVIDIA. This will change in "
"the future when the NVIDIA driver supports Optimus."
msgstr ""

#: ../../preinstall.rst:178
msgid ""
"|trueos| has built-in support for most wireless networking cards. |trueos| "
"will automatically detect available wireless networks for supported wireless"
" devices. Verify the device is supported by clicking :guilabel:`Hardware "
"Compatibility` within the installer. If it is an external wireless device, "
"insert it before running the installer."
